<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_77_r1l18">Edler lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / als wır nehſt auf eẅr ſchrift vnd <expan>begeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> dıe Jr an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l19"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> gut freẅnde des Rats ʒu Eger getan habt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıener <expan>Burkarte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l20"><expan>Reıkarcʒhof<ex>er</ex></expan> gen Eger geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> hat vns wol geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l21">vvıe Jm <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> daſelbs von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ercʒelt ıſt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> . dar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_77_r1l22"><expan>ynn<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> daʒ eẅr edel auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteet</expan> / vvıe wır vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
